      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23636185&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=732&rangeEnd=773",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9bd323607168a8d99bd5f3e?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=732&rangeEnd=773"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "23636185_6_2839-2904",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "2839-2904",
      "markText": "“吉普赛人在战争中都做什么呢？”罗伯特·乔丹问他。 “就继续当吉普赛人。”",
      "totalCount": 170,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23636185&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2839&rangeEnd=2904",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9bd323607168a8d99bd5f3e?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=2839&rangeEnd=2904"
    },
    {
