      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "4146-4197",
      "markText": "还有，你得确定能相信谁。要么完全相信你的同伴，要么完全不信，没有别的选择。你必须在信任问题上做出决定。",
      "totalCount": 165,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=23636185&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4146&rangeEnd=4197",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/9bd323607168a8d99bd5f3e?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=4146&rangeEnd=4197"
    },
    {
